data.description: Welcome to your dream! This beautiful townhouse has been lovingly cared for and maintained. As you enter you are greeted by the hardwood floors and cozy feel. On the main floor you will find a spacious bedroom and a half bath for your guests. The open concept main floor is perfect for entertaining guests or yourself, not to mention the beautiful marsh views out of the windows. Off the dining area you will have a marvelous airy porch that overlooks the beautiful live oaks and the calm swaying marsh grass. Going upstairs there are two bedrooms with their own full bathrooms, one of these being the master bed and bath. The master features a roomy walk in closet, dual vanities, a soaking tub, and a separate shower. The 2.5 car garage downstairs is perfect for storing all of your extra items!
